<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />When evildoers approached me to devour my flesh,</para>

<para style="q1">my adversaries and my enemies stumbled and fell.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Though an army encamps against me,</para>

<para style="q1">my heart will not fear;</para>

<para style="q1">though war rises up against me,</para>

<para style="q1">even then I will remain confident.</para>
